  "contenu": [
    {
      "id": "8614e838-6985-4f01-85b5-abaf5ca23548",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $f \\colon \\R^2 \\to \\R$,\n$$ (x,y) \\mapsto \\dfrac{x^2 y^2}{x^2 y^2 + (x-y)^2} $$",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f \\colon \\R^2 \\to \\R\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math display\">\\[(x,y) \\mapsto \\dfrac{x^2 y^2}{x^2 y^2 +\n(x-y)^2}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b7859d6e-9a9f-42c5-994b-8459a07de371",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Donner l'ensemble de définition de $f$.",
        "html": "<p>Donner l’ensemble de définition de <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9dfe8845-e031-4a85-ab16-7c46bb5a4723",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "La fonction $f$ est définie pour tout $(x,y)\\in \\R^2$ tels que $x^2 y^2 + (x-y)^2 \\neq 0 $. Or $x^2y^2 + (x-y)^2 = 0 \\iff xy = 0 \\text{ et } x=y \\iff x=y=0$ donc $f$ est définie sur $\\R^2 \\backslash \\{(0,0)\\}$.",
        "html": "<p>La fonction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est définie pour\ntout <span class=\"math inline\">\\((x,y)\\in \\R^2\\)</span> tels que <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x^2 y^2 + (x-y)^2 \\neq 0\\)</span>. Or <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x^2y^2 + (x-y)^2 = 0 \\iff xy = 0 \\text{ et } x=y\n\\iff x=y=0\\)</span> donc <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est\ndéfinie sur <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\R^2 \\backslash\n\\{(0,0)\\}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "31493fa7-ade1-4257-a32e-24bb4fdfc938",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour $x$ fixé, calculer $g(x) = \\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} f(x,y)$.",
        "html": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x\\)</span> fixé, calculer <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(g(x) = \\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} f(x,y)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "66b535d6-d825-4039-99b3-d3d964f86402",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $x \\in \\R$ : si $x=0$, $f(0,y) = 0$ et si $x \\neq 0$, $f(x,y) \\xrightarrow[y \\to 0]{} \\frac{0}{x^2} = 0$",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x \\in \\R\\)</span> : si <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x=0\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(0,y) =\n0\\)</span> et si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x \\neq 0\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,y) \\xrightarrow[y \\to 0]{} \\frac{0}{x^2} =\n0\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4d842b4d-2fec-4dd4-b8f0-71be59b94577",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour $y$ fixé, calculer $h(y) = \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} f(x,y)$.",
        "html": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(y\\)</span> fixé, calculer <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(h(y) = \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} f(x,y)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a122625d-308e-4760-b149-f17e5b19de7c",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "De même, $h(y) = 0$.",
        "html": "<p>De même, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(h(y) = 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "64d52f57-896c-4c55-93d3-4ea0d004aa5c",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} g(x)$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0}\ng(x)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f43f2e4e-5d66-4f7d-81f9-8e0a4ed6fa9e",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On en déduit que $\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} g(x) = 0$",
        "html": "<p>On en déduit que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0}\ng(x) = 0\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "54395f95-879a-4f33-8227-e9b3d0a72d26",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} h(y)$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0}\nh(y)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5d905ffc-eb0d-4665-9ee9-4018a3004e58",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "De même $\\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} h(y) = 0$",
        "html": "<p>De même <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim\\limits_{y \\to 0} h(y) =\n0\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "dce3c8dc-fce6-4fee-8154-c57e9856b4d2",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "La fonction $f$ admet-elle une limite quand $(x,y) \\to (0,0)$~?",
        "html": "<p>La fonction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> admet-elle une\nlimite quand <span class=\"math inline\">\\((x,y) \\to (0,0)\\)</span> ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f68bedc7-921b-4aac-9c87-135d78f0a9c1",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Non car $f(x,x) = 1 \\xrightarrow[x \\to 0]{} 1$ et $f(x,0) = 0 \\xrightarrow[x \\to 0]{} 0 \\neq 1$ : on a deux chemins qui donnent deux limites différentes.",
        "html": "<p>Non car <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,x) = 1 \\xrightarrow[x \\to\n0]{} 1\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x,0) = 0 \\xrightarrow[x\n\\to 0]{} 0 \\neq 1\\)</span> : on a deux chemins qui donnent deux limites\ndifférentes.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
}